rozny-late-on-October-5-2011.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2011 年 10 月 5 日晚，车臣领导人拉姆赞·卡德罗夫（右）在格罗兹尼的一场表演中跳舞。（照片来源应为 STR/AFP via Getty Images）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-leader-Ramzan-Kadyrov-R-dances-during-a-performance-in-Grozny-late-on-October-5-2011.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-leader-Ramzan-Kadyrov-R-dances-during-a-performance-in-Grozny-late-on-October-5-2011-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-leader-Ramzan-Kadyrov-R-dances-during-a-performance-in-Grozny-late-on-October-5-2011-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-leader-Ramzan-Kadyrov-R-dances-during-a-performance-in-Grozny-late-on-October-5-2011-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-leader-Ramzan-Kadyrov-R-dances-during-a-performance-in-Grozny-late-on-October-5-2011-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-leader-Ramzan-Kadyrov-R-dances-during-a-performance-in-Grozny-late-on-October-5-2011-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，车臣当局禁止了他们认为“太快或太慢”的音乐。</p><p>据俄罗斯国家通讯社塔斯社（ <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2024/04/08/europe/chechnya-music-ban-scli-intl/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>CNN</em></a> ）报道，文化部长穆萨·达达耶夫表示：“（我）已宣布与车臣共和国总统拉姆赞·阿赫马托维奇·卡德罗夫达成一致的最终决定，从现在开始，所有音乐、声乐编舞作品必须对应每分钟80到116拍的节奏。”</p><p>达达耶夫补充说，这一决定将确保车臣音乐和舞蹈创作符合“车臣心态和音乐节奏”，旨在为“人民和我们孩子的未来带来车臣人民的文化遗产”。</p><p>每分钟 80 到 116 拍的节奏相对较慢，与当今大多数现代流行音乐不同。这一决定将禁止各种西方音乐流派在公共场合播放。 </p><figure id="attachment_3614973" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3614973" style="width: 2700px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3614973" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-President-Ramsan-Kadyrov-dances-with-a-woman.jpg" alt="2007 年 3 月 8 日，车臣总统拉姆桑·卡德罗夫在格罗兹尼机场等待首趟航班时与一位女士跳舞。（照片来源应为 DMITRY NIKOFOROV/AFP via Getty Images）" width="2700" height="1351" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-President-Ramsan-Kadyrov-dances-with-a-woman.jpg 2700w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-President-Ramsan-Kadyrov-dances-with-a-woman-400x200.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-President-Ramsan-Kadyrov-dances-with-a-woman-800x400.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-President-Ramsan-Kadyrov-dances-with-a-woman-696x348.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-President-Ramsan-Kadyrov-dances-with-a-woman-1392x697.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chechen-President-Ramsan-Kadyrov-dances-with-a-woman-1068x534.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2700px) 100vw, 2700px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3614973" class="wp-caption-text"> 2007 年 3 月 8 日，车臣总统拉姆桑·卡德罗夫在格罗兹尼机场等待首趟航班时与一位女士跳舞。（照片来源应为 DMITRY NIKOFOROV/AFP via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>根据新规定，BPM 较高的西方乌鸦音乐和电子音乐也将被禁止公开播放。</p><p>据<a href="https://news.sky.com/story/chechnya-bans-music-that-is-too-fast-or-too-slow-13110266" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>天空新闻报道</em></a>，音乐禁令是在共和国部门与当地和地区艺术家举行会议后宣布的。据报道，艺术家们被要求在 6 月 1 日之前重写不符合标准的音乐。</p><p>其他新闻方面，车臣一直是俄罗斯入侵乌克兰的公开支持者，近年来反 LGBTQ+ 暴力事件大量涌入。</p><p>据报道，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京 (Vladamir Putin) 已责成科技公司开发一款能够与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X/S</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/putin-has-given-russian-developers-until-june-to-create-a-playstation-and-xbox-rival-3613824">相媲美的游戏机</a>。</p><p>据俄罗斯报纸<em><a href="https://www.kommersant.ru/doc/6595900" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《生意人报》</a></em> （来自<em><a href="https://readwrite.com/putin-pushes-for-russian-rival-to-ps5-and-xbox-game-consoles/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ReadWrite</a></em> ）报道，克里姆林宫已<a href="http://kremlin.ru/acts/assignments/orders/73743" target="_blank" rel="noopener">命令</a>俄罗斯开发商“考虑组织固定式和便携式游戏机的生产问题”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chechnya-bans-music-that-is-too-fast-or-too-slow-3614925">车臣“禁止太快或太慢的音乐”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
